ve%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20water%20crisis.%20It%20was%20very%20evident%20since%20April%20that%20Delhi%20would%20face%20prolonged%20extreme%20heat.%20I%20question%20why%20the%20Delhi%20government%20did%20not%20implement%20a%20'Summer%20Action%20Plan'%20and%20failed%20to%20prepare%20for%20this%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Delhi%20minister's%20Haryana%20argument%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20often%20blame%20Haryana%20for%20water%2C%20so%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20why%20don't%20they%20source%20water%20from%20their%20ruling%20state%20Punjab%20or%20their%20coalition%20state%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%3F%20They%20can't%20even%20give%20a%20single%20line%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20of%20what%20efforts%20they%20made%20to%20meet%20the%20water%20demands%20of%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20maximum%20temperature%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20is%20inching%20close%20to%20the%2050%20degrees%20Celsius%20mark.%20The%20minimum%20temperature%20is%20nearly%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%202.8%20degrees%20above%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20said%20heatwave%20conditions%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20will%20persist%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days%20and%20advised%20people%20to%20minimise%20exposure%20to%20heat%20and%20stay%20hydrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716976860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffedjljf8_water-shortage-generic-water-tanker-generic-ani_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-shortage-in-delhi-rs-2-000-fine-for-washing-car-with-hose-5770673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Washing%20cars%20with%20hose%2C%20using%20domestic%20supply%20for%20commercial%20purposes%20and%20overflowing%20water%20tanks%20in%20Delhi%20will%20attract%20a%20Rs%202%2C000%20fine%20as%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20takes%20urgent%20steps%