al%20we%20had%20a%20fox-themed%20nursery%20when%20Copper%20was%20born.%20Though%20the%20decor%20wasn't%20planned%20until%20my%20pregnancy%2C%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-names-relatives-legacy-tradition-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edecided%20on%20his%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20long%20before%20his%20birth.%20Just%20months%20after%20we%20were%20married%2C%20my%20husband%20put%20on%20the%20film.%20(His%20love%20of%20cereal%20and%20cartoons%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20ways%20he's%20a%20child%20at%20heart.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BCopper%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20watching.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20it.%20If%20we%20have%20a%20boy%2C%20that%20will%20be%20his%20name.%26quot%3B%20I%20laughed%20it%20off%2C%20not%20ready%20to%20make%20that%20decision%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20I%20quickly%20forgot%20about%20the%20conversation.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20when%20I%20was%20actually%20pregnant%20with%20a%20boy%2C%20he%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20choice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20sat%20on%20it%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%20deciding%20if%20I%20liked%20it%20enough%20to%20give%20it%20to%20our%20child.%20I%20didn't%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20like%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20cute%20and%20different%20without%20being%20strange.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20spelled%20like%20it's%20pronounced%2C%20which%20is%20my%20biggest%20rule%20for%20choosing%20a%20name%20for%20our%20child.%20Like%20any%20other%20parent%2C%20I%20want%20things%20to%20be%20easy%20for%20my%20kids%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20them%20having%20to%20spend%20their%20time%20and%20energy%20teaching%20people%20how%20to%20say%20or%20spell%20their%20name.%20(After%20all%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funusual-name-social-anxiety-kid-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eteach%20people%20to%20spell%20my%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20my%20entire%20life%2C%20and%20I%20know%20what%20it's%20like.)%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20grew%20on%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20I%20was%20even%20six%20months%20pregnant%2C%20we%20had%20decided%20on%20his%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232cfc782-cd29-4f80-b76c-25816ecc754d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20every%20nurse%20gets%20it%20wrong%20on%20the%20first%20try%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe's%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BCooper%26quot%3B%20by%20every%20nurse%20at%20every%20doctor's%20office%20we%20have%20ever%20attended.%20(And%20countless%20others.)%20When%20they%20call%20him%20back%20to%20take%20his%20vitals%2C%20if%20it's%20a%20new%20nurse%2C%20they%20call%20out%20the%20more%20common%20%26quot%3BCooper.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20they%20only%20make%20the%20mistake%20the%20first%20time%3B%20once%20I%20correct%20them%20(politely)%2C%20it's%20a%20name%20no%20one%20forgets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20laugh%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYep%2C%20that's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-common-name-people-cant-spell-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehow%20it's%20spelled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20just%20wasn't%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20something%20to%20that%20effect.%20And%20to%20their%20credit%2C%20you%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ecan't%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20always%20be%20sure%20that%20just%20because%20a%20name%20looks%20like%20it's%20pronounced%20one%20way%2C%20it's%20not%20pronounced%20another%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20unsure%2C%20it's%20always%20better%20to%20ask.%20But%20I%20digress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20the%20above%2C%20in%20part%2C%20is%20why%20we%20chose%20the%20safer%20(and%20admittedly%2C%20more%20boring)%20name%20Colt%20for%20his%20younger%20brother.%20Ironically%2C%20Colt%20i