.27.44-PM-1716887034.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221021%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anchal%20Bhateja's%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034.jpeg%201021w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-239x300.jpeg%20239w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-500x627.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-768x963.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351293%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnchal%20Bhateja%E2%80%99s%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInclusivity%20IRL%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20disability%20inclusion%20journey%20at%20her%20organisation%2C%20Seema%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20human%20resources%20manager%20based%20out%20of%20Delhi%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CIncluding%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20helped%20the%20organisation%20in%20several%20unintended%20ways.%20Beyond%20just%20creating%20a%20more%20equitable%20workforce%2C%20having%20PwDs%20at%20the%20workplace%20has%20helped%20us%20relook%20at%20our%20policies%2C%20processes%20and%20infrastructure%20from%20a%20new%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20employers%20warm%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20employing%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20also%20moving%20towards%20becoming%20a%20more%20inclusive%20space%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20this%20sentiment%2C%20Amar%20Jain%2C%20a%20visually%20impaired%20lawyer%20and%20accessibility%20professional%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20lawyer%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20we%20face%20enormous%20barriers.%20The%20data%20provided%20by%20clients%20is%20not%20accessible%2C%20the%20physical%20case%20files%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20digital%20copies.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20progressive%20steps%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20judicial%20system.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20recently%20released%20a%20mandate%20to%20provide%20digital%20copies%20of%20case%20files%20to%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20landscape%20is%20changing%2C%20slowly%20but%20surely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20understanding%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%20Anchal%20interned%20at%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20chambers%20as%20a%20student.%20She%20remembers%20how%20forthcoming%20they%20were%20with%20respect%20to%20offering%20%E2%80%98Reasonable%20Accommodations%E2%80%99%20to%20help%20her%20work%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20make%20case%20briefs%20with%20page%20number%20references.%20As%20a%20visually-impaired%20person%2C%20it%20is%20sometimes%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20right%20page%20number%2C%20so%20I%20use%20paragraph%20numbers%20instead%20and%20this%20request%20of%20mine%20was%20accommodated%20and%20helped%20me%20better%20do%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%20also%20recollects%20how%20she%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20upon%20completing%20the%20internship%20in%20his%20chamber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20me%20that%20my%20research%20skills%20were%20remarkable%20and%20that%20he%20faced%20no%20challenges%20in%20using%20the%20briefs%20prepared%20by%20me.%20He%20was%20also%20an%20understanding%20senior%20as%20he%20was%20open%20to%20me%20working%20in%20my%20own%20way%20and%20using%20slightly%20different%20formats%20to%20present%20my%20briefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAanchal%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20more%20than%20just%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20triumph%20over%20adversity%2C%20it%20is%20a%20powerful%20call%20to%20action%20for%20building%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20society.%20By%20promoting%20accessibility%20awareness%20and%20implementing%20robust%20support%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20empower%20everyone%20regardless%20of%20ability%20to%20reach%20their%20full%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343534%2Fsparsh-asian-paints-start-foundation-initiative-tactile-art-rajasthan-netraheen-kalyan-sangh-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20with%20diverse%20disabilities%20benefit%20from%20digital%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20can%20be%20found%20in%20a%20number%20of%20different%20forms.%20From%20adaptive%20keyboards%20to%20speech%20to%20text%20softwares%2C%20technology%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20finding%20ways%20to%20accommodate%20human%20diversity%2C%20all%20that%20is%20remaining%20is%20a%20sincere%20effort%20from%20us%20to%20integrate%20it%20into%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20V-shesh%2C%20edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716888992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anchal%20Bhateja%20lost%20her%20eyesight%20just%20before%20her%20board%20exams.%20She%20chose%20to%20keep%20her%20dreams%20alive%20and%20wo