ning%2C%20smaller%20investments%20translate%20to%20smaller%20risks.%20Coming%20from%20a%20humble%20background%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CInvest%20a%20minimal%20amount%20in%20the%20sector.%20Always%20keep%20these%20two%20points%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20homegrown%20business%2C%20so%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20see%20better%20results%2C%20and%20never%20expect%20to%20make%20a%20profit%20in%20a%20month%20or%20two.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Know%20your%20market%20and%20consumers%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConduct%20market%20research%2C%20analyse%20competitors%2C%20and%20gather%20feedback%20to%20alter%20your%20menu%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20pricing%20for%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20consider%20factors%20such%20as%20ingredient%20costs%2C%20labour%2C%20overhead%20expenses%2C%20market%20demand%2C%20and%20perceived%20value.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20profitability%20and%20affordability%20while%20ensuring%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20offerings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raji%20advises%20to%20invest%20small%20amount%20to%20avoid%20losses%20when%20setting%20up%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20in%20India.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045-768x402.jpg%207