g%20Room%2C%20Sculpture%20Room%2C%20Billiards%20Room%20and%20%3Cem%3EThakur%20Dalan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(place%20of%20worship).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20these%20rooms%20bears%20the%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20art%20that%20Rajendra%20collected%20along%20his%20travels.%20He%20loved%20dabbling%20in%20it%3B%20the%20Bohemian%20goblets%2C%20French%20Ormulo%20clocks%2C%20swords%20from%20Toledo%2C%20and%20Venetian%20mirrors%20are%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F146531%2Fnews-world-ethnic-day-15-must-have-ethnic-souvenirs-from-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esouvenirs%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren%E2%80%99t%20delighting%20your%20senses%2C%20huge%20oil%20paintings%20will.%20These%20include%20Rubens%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98The%20Marriage%20of%20St%20Catherine%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Infant%20Hercules%20Strangling%20the%20Serpent%E2%80%99%20by%20Joshua%20Reynolds%2C%20paintings%20by%20Raja%20Ravi%20Varma%2C%20Jan%20Van%20Goyen%2C%20and%20Giovanni%20Battista%2C%20and%20sculptures%20of%20Venus%2C%20Apollo%2C%20Homer%2C%20and%20other%20mythical%20and%20real%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20the%20palace%20houses%2076%20rare%20artworks%20brought%20from%20Italy%20and%20Belgium%20in%201830%2C%20and%20a%20two-cornered%20biocome%20that%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20worn%20by%20Napoleon%20Bonaparte%20during%20his%20military%20campaigns.%20The%20originality%20is%20still%20debated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20way%20will%20be%20illuminated%20by%20the%20light%20bouncing%20off%20the%2019th-century%20disco%20balls.%20The%20palace%20is%20a%20balance%20between%20grandeur%20and%20a%20warm%20place%20called%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99.%20But%20while%20it%20is%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20touch%20for%20artefacts%20that%20draws%20visitors%20to%20the%20place%2C%20it%20was%20once%20the%20zoo%20that%20made%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%