0Bengaluru%20Restaurant%20Serves%20Free%20Dosas%20to%20Those%20Who%20Vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20a%20billion%20eligible%20voters%2C%20India%20is%20undergoing%20the%20biggest%20general%20elections%20in%20the%20world.%20While%20our%20dedicated%20election%20officers%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20bring%20democracy%20to%20our%20doorstep%2C%20citizens%20eagerly%20line%20up%20to%20exercise%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20polling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54110%2Ffirst-transgender-polling-booth-officer-riya-sarkar%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eday%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20city%20witnessed%20two%20notable%20queues%3A%20one%20at%20the%20polling%20station%20and%20another%20at%20a%20local%20restaurant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20made%20this%20restaurant%20stand%20out%3F%20Most%20of%20the%20weary%20voters%20were%20lining%20up%20outside%20Nisarga%20Grand%20Hotel%20for%20their%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20juice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20who%20they%20voted%20for%2C%20just%20that%20they%20did.%20We%20served%20over%206%2C000%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20polling%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20SP%20Krishnaraj%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20hotel%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurious%20about%20why%20a%20man%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20serving%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20Join%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20as%20we%20delve%20into%20his%20heartwarming%20journey%20and%20discover%20where%20it%20all%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIt%20all%20started%20with%20an%20angry%20young%20man%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnaraj%20worked%20with%20different%20restaurants%20before%20opening%20his%20own%20place%20in%202017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20been%20in%20the%20business%20of%20restaurants%20working%20for%20different%20places%20but%20opening%20my%20own%20restaurant%20was%20my%20biggest%20dream.%20After%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20open%20Nisarga%20Grand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20his%20restaurant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20days%20were%20not%20as%20grand%20as%20I%20had%20hoped%20for%20them%20to%20be.%20But%20what%20I%20focussed%20on%20was%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20eatery%20has%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000%20free%20dosas%20since%202018.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350696%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20eatery%20has%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Esince%202018.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20he%20started%20chatting%20with%20a%20young%20guest.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20back%20in%202018%20and%20the%20elections%20were%20going%20on.%20I%20started%20to%20chat%20with%20the%20young%20man%20and%20noticed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20voted.%20I%20inquired%20why%20and%20he%20simply%20said%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20questioning%2C%20Krishnaraj%20realised%20that%20he%20did%20not%20like%20any%20parties%20contesting%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20they%20all%20are%20the%20same%20and%20he%20had%20no%20faith%20in%20any%20leader.%20I%20proceeded%20to%20make%20him%20understand%20that%20voting%20is%20a%20right%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20exercise.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20uphold%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20started%20to%20have%20a%20discussion%20and%20the%20man%20casually%20mentioned%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F37260%2Fdifferently-abled-friendly-polling-stations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20and%20vote%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyou%20will%20have%20to%20give%20me%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20he%20was%20joking%20but%20I%20readily%20agreed%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20vote.%20He%20did%20show%20up%20some%20hours%20later%20with%20an%20inked%20finger.%20I%20gave%20him%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20juice%20that%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnaraj%20kept%20replaying%20the%20incident%20and%20realised%20that%20there%20must%20be%20many%20more%20people%20like%20that%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20patriot%20and%20have%20wanted%20to%20do%20my%20part%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20growth.%20In%20society%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20highest%20entity%20and%20everyone%20should%20follow%20it.%20The%20incident%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishn