20doctor%E2%80%99s%20advice%20and%20got%20back%20a%20money%20plant-cutting%20to%20start%20her%20gardening%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20my%20relatives%20are%20farmers%20and%20also%20grow%20plants%20at%20home.%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20gardening%20tips%20and%20started%20my%20journey%20%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETending%20to%20the%20money%20plant%20gave%20the%20gardener%20the%20confidence%20to%20try%20growing%20more%20plants.%20She%20ventured%20into%20growing%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20which%20she%20would%20feed%20her%20son%20daily.%20Later%2C%20she%20added%20more%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%20and%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20vegetables%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20easy%2C%20she%20discovered%2C%20as%20she%20encountered%20many%20failures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20one%20harvest%20of%20tomatoes%20but%20the%20next%20one%20would%20fail.%20I%20referred%20to%20several%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20learn%20the%20ropes%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20experience%20is%20the%20biggest%20teacher.%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20when%20and%20how%20often%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20give%20fertiliser.%20How%20much%20direct%20sunlight%20should%20be%20given%20was%20also%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20she%20learnt%20that%20it%20was%20ideal%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20early%20morning%2C%20between%207%20to%208%20am%2C%20the%20best%20time%20to%20do%20pest%20control%20was%20either%20before%206%20am%20or%20after%206%20pm%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20generally%20need%20more%20water.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20each%20vegetable%2C%20flower%20and%20fruit%20was%20different%2C%20and%20she%20would%20have%20to%20work%20her%20way%20around%20that%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGardening%20as%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAft